690
00:30:35,100 --> 00:30:35,620
Why?

691
00:30:36,860 --> 00:30:39,100
His condition is getting worse.

692
00:30:39,860 --> 00:30:41,710
He'll die anytime.

693
00:30:42,710 --> 00:30:43,230
Moreover,

