697
00:30:52,470 --> 00:30:52,860
Upheaval?

698
00:30:54,790 --> 00:30:56,340
When have you ever been afraid of upheaval?

699
00:30:57,510 --> 00:30:58,270
Isn't that

700
00:30:58,270 --> 00:30:59,070
what you always wanted?

