835
00:36:07,830 --> 00:36:09,100
He'll drag the entire Langya Army

836
00:36:10,710 --> 00:36:11,830
and Xiao Lingchen down.

837
00:36:13,460 --> 00:36:14,670
Even if he wins in the end,

838
00:36:15,980 --> 00:36:17,310
